description: The investment seeks to track the investment results of the Bloomberg Barclays December 2020 Maturity Corporate Index (the "underlying index"). The fund generally will invest at least 90% of its assets in the component securities of the underlying index. The underlying index is composed of U.S. dollar-denominated, taxable, investment-grade corporate bonds scheduled to mature after December 31, 2019 and before December 16, 2020.
name: iShares iBonds Dec 2020 Term Corporate ETF
